  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">There are <math alttext=\"450\"><mn>450</mn>\n</math> tiles in a box. Of these tiles, <math alttext=\"6 percent sign\"><mn>6</mn><mo>%</mo></math> are black. How many black tiles are in the box?</p>",
